UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1948
1 officials in both the Democratic and Republican Parties of Kentucky; and
2 WHEREAS, The Links, Incorporated continues to be a vital institution and a pillar
3 of this great Nation and the Commonwealth;
4 NOW, THEREFORE,
5 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
6 Kentucky:
7 Section 1. The Senate recognizes The Links, Incorporated Day at the State
8 Capitol, February 26, 2026, and welcomes the members of the Kentucky chapters of this
9 national organization who are visiting the Capitol today.
10 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
11 Resolution to Senator Gerald Neal for presentation.
